name: Rejuve.AI
description: Rejuve.AI is a decentralized, AI-driven longevity research network allowing people from all over the world to track their health data, receive valuable insights, contribute to cutting-edge longevity research, and earn rewards. Rejuve.AI's primary research tool is the Longevity mobile app (iOS and Android), allowing users to track their health data, receive a biological age calculation and valuable health insights, access top of the line health products and services, and have an opportunity to earn RJV for contributing their data to longevity research.
